		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't have an SNES PowerPak, but the flash chip should be hooked like the same as a RAM chip would be (with a /write signal connected).  I've uploaded some code that works with an AMD flash chip, I'm sure it would work on SNES with the Atmel flash chip with little (if any) modification.<br /><a href="http://membler-industries.com/nes/flash.asm" class="postlink">http://membler-industries.com/nes/flash.asm</a>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
